insurance adjusters tally the damage from Hurricane Floyd, a
growing chorus of authorities says Americans have mainly themselves
and their government to blame for the rising cost of ``acts of
God.'' By Scott Allen. 1800 words. GRAPHIC: 25 picas x 6 inches,
``Subsidizing victims.''
