said Vladimir Polyakov, a Gorbachev spokesman.
</P>
<P>
   President Boris Yeltsin, Gorbachev's bitter rival in the early
1990s, sent a message of condolence Monday, and in a statement, he
said, that a ``wonderful person, a beautiful woman, a loving wife
and mother is no longer with us.''
</P>
