<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-20 19:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9274 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i BC-CAMPAIGN-MCCAIN-BOS &LR;      09-20 0793
