<P>
   &UR; TOTAL _  &LR; People who own shares in mutual funds that track the
Standard &AMP; Poor's 500 index have enjoyed great returns in recent
years _ but t now experts are suggesting that it may be time for
these share holders to hedge their bets with broader-based index
funds. BY ARTHUR M. LOUIS.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; MONEYBAG _  &LR; finance Q&AMP;A column. BY ARTHUR M. LOUIS.
