-- Sen. Barbara Boxer, D-Calif., says that companies drilling on
federal land are underpaying. ``We shouldn't have a double standard
just because an oil company is powerful, just because an oil
company can give millions of dollars in contributions,'' she says.
(Edward Carreon/New York Times Photo) LITE
