<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-20 22:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9420 &Cx1f; taf-z
s t BC-PRACTICAL-TRAVELER-2T     09-20 0943
